name: Dynamic Credit Opportunities Fund
longDescription: To achieve the Funds investment objectives, the Fund will followa comprehensive top-down and bottom-up investment process focused on the risk-reward relationship of individual credit investments inside a diversified portfolio. Dynamic Credit Opportunities Fund ETF seeks to generate absolute return over a complete market cycle through long and short positions in primarily coporate debt securities.
